     SHORT="kmldonkey integrates MLDonkey into KDE."
      LONG="
kmldonkey integrate MLDonkey into KDE. 
It provides the following features:

 * ED2K link handling in Konqueror
 * Konqueror service menu for adding all links 
   on a web page
 * Control Centre module for configuring how to 
   talk to MLDonkey
 * A panel applet for Kicker that displays mldonkey 
   status
---
The scripts are known to work with MLDonkey 1.16 and 2.0+.
"
